item.title: CVE-2019-10410|2024-08-04T22:24:16.967Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20log%20parser%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Log Parser Plugin 2.0 and earlier did not escape an error message, resulting in a cross-site scripting vulnerability exploitable by users able to define log parsing rules.
